Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.35,0:00:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新机动战记-钢弹W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.55,0:00:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.02,0:00:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.56,0:00:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.67,0:00:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱着你被淋湿的肩膀 想温暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.88,0:00:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,颤抖的指尖 彷徨地在找什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.68,0:00:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的视线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.96,0:01:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲伤变为力量的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.40,0:01:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.07,0:01:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.71,0:01:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.41,0:01:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.15,0:01:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父亲大人!请你快逃走!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.92,0:01:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔，我在逃避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.06,0:01:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绝对不是在战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.53,0:01:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗没有终结
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.86,0:01:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我在逃避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.00,0:01:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果因此要我死，那也没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.00,0:01:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用为了留恋宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.00,0:01:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连自己的生活方式改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.00,0:01:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父亲大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.35,0:01:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父亲大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.29,0:01:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父亲大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.33,0:02:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十二话\N[争取独立之战]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.81,0:02:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好大啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.01,0:02:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亲善大使是个怎样的人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.88,0:02:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.11,0:02:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那部机动战士是在地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.98,0:02:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和Oz敌对的机体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.75,0:02:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我们要先检查一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.37,0:02:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由于宇宙卫星和Oz合并
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.21,0:02:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙的形势对地球影响很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.64,0:02:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我以一个国家的代表身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.18,0:03:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前来这里打听那方面的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.08,0:03:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一个国家?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.38,0:03:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我忘了自我介绍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.02,0:03:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是山克王国的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.39,0:03:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米利亚尔特‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.99,0:03:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你从大人自小就有交情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.56,0:03:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王国前来?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.56,0:03:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有听闻\N在今次战乱中开始复兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.63,0:03:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想知道战争会带来什么的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.80,0:03:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能向想拥有武力的卫星荐言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.37,0:03:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寻求和平有很多方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.91,0:03:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起学习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.91,0:03:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就能朝着更好的方向前进吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.85,0:03:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.88,0:03:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可以让我\N在宇宙自由行动吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.49,0:03:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.22,0:03:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你或许正在走\N一条的明智的路呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.32,0:03:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.26,0:03:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,匹斯克拉福特?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.76,0:03:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙不是Oz的叛徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.50,0:03:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯‧马吉斯吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.90,0:03:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙卫星D120
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.83,0:03:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是以前地球圈统一联合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.04,0:03:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙司令部的所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.77,0:04:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oz现在没有进行武力镇压
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.61,0:04:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并劝他们加入卫星议会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.38,0:04:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,D120方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.15,0:04:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放弃了地球军事组织的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.38,0:04:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直站在代表地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.85,0:04:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,于宇宙的意向的立场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.89,0:04:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,旧联合宇宙军司令官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.42,0:04:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赛普提姆将军的儿子金达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.53,0:04:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是这个卫星的代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.49,0:04:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在他身边的旧联合的人认为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.93,0:04:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oz从后推动的卫星独立政策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.50,0:04:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是个严重问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.00,0:04:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还在犹豫什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.10,0:04:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在，Oz想拥有更强大的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.51,0:04:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不战斗不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.21,0:04:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙的科技\N对地球只会造成威胁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.21,0:04:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oz只是把宇宙当作军事工厂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.95,0:04:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在能消灭他们的只有我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.79,0:04:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是我们的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.82,0:04:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗会产生许多牺牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.19,0:04:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以我们现在的兵力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.03,0:04:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也能考虑和他们谈判
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.46,0:04:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们想把宇宙用来\N开发MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.30,0:04:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杀人兵器会令Oz做出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.03,0:05:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,极其简单的独裁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.27,0:05:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位全部有同一想法吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.04,0:05:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯‧马吉斯来了宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.32,0:05:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,害怕宇宙武装起来的是地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.82,0:05:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们可以抽时间听听熟识Oz
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.95,0:05:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望地球和平的他的意见吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.96,0:05:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,离开Oz的杰克斯.马吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.29,0:05:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为何来到这个宇宙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.10,0:05:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是个热爱祖国的男子汉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.43,0:05:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他知道无人行动就会出现危机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.50,0:05:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是有意义的行动啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.54,0:05:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯‧克修里那达\N你果然厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.04,0:05:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙正逐渐认同Oz
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.74,0:05:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.01,0:05:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安特校的表现很出色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.88,0:05:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她陆续和卫星建立起友好关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.82,0:05:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在宇宙建立国家的独立心态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.99,0:05:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会生出生产性和防卫意识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.93,0:06:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后以军事国家的身份站起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.76,0:06:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球的各国感到威胁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.10,0:06:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就会争先恐后寻求Oz的支配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.17,0:06:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了不起，特列斯，想不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.57,0:06:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你把宇宙变为罗姆斐拉的一份子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.17,0:06:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.91,0:06:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兹巴洛夫，准备好了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.11,0:06:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.24,0:06:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了强化宇宙的军备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.78,0:06:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兹巴洛夫会前去生产MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.12,0:06:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安特校也爽快地同意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.02,0:06:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安她…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.19,0:06:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.72,0:06:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来非常喜欢MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.16,0:06:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人，久违了，我是蕾蒂‧安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.87,0:06:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.37,0:06:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是想着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.04,0:06:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和兹巴洛夫技师\N一起前来的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.87,0:06:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是那件事，蕾蒂‧安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.24,0:06:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你打算怎样处置MD?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.75,0:06:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会把它们用作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.38,0:06:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会令大人你痛心的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.85,0:06:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的士兵?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.95,0:07:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人你真狡猾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.09,0:07:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人你一定要站在世界的最高处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.03,0:07:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但你把这世界弃于混乱中不顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.90,0:07:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我为了协助大人你上来宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.87,0:07:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且为大人准备未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.24,0:07:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗不会从这世上消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.07,0:07:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，强者永远统治世界就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.21,0:07:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们被强者支配觉得高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.95,0:07:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世上继续战斗是当然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.89,0:07:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那样会白流太多的血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.72,0:07:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人你爱着所有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.86,0:07:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拥有能成为神的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.53,0:07:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能从宇宙为地球建立和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.36,0:07:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂\N你正以自己的理想看未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.74,0:07:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那也是大人你所希望的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.87,0:07:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的理想只是一个人类的妄想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.21,0:07:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,历史由日子累积而成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.15,0:08:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它对个人的未来无兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.58,0:08:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人你的未来已经早有定论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.05,0:08:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙才有大人你的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.35,0:08:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂，我并非那么坚强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.76,0:08:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯和钢弹的驾驶员们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.39,0:08:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正在创造未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.60,0:08:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不须要回头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.50,0:08:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,时代会重覆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.50,0:08:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂，变回以前那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.77,0:08:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,变回我以前好喜欢的蕾蒂‧安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.55,0:08:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会有错，是杰克斯‧马吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.85,0:08:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯在宇宙出现了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.95,0:08:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他企图和旧联合的\N军事卫星接触
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.22,0:08:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尼哥尔特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.46,0:08:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消灭旧联合宇宙军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.79,0:08:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然已经完成MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.79,0:08:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就不用让他们生存下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.06,0:08:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.36,0:08:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.66,0:08:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要给蕾蒂‧安特校\N今后的指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.87,0:08:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告诉她我想要她的确认报告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.30,0:08:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.28,0:09:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,欢迎光临，虽然我们曾是敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.48,0:09:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但战争时代又令我们见面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.65,0:09:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和关怀地球的联合\N有同一立场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.59,0:09:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听闻你为了宇宙卫星武装一事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.49,0:09:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从地球前来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.83,0:09:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果只是诞生新的军事国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.20,0:09:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我并不觉得问题那么严重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.13,0:09:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，如果他们被Oz瞒骗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.77,0:09:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就不可以袖手旁观
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.60,0:09:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oz想把宇宙用作军事工场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.48,0:09:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此，地球的纷争会加剧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.78,0:09:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那会产生许多牺牲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.45,0:09:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙的人有何看法?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.18,0:09:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,匹斯克拉福特先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.05,0:09:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死去的领导人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.79,0:09:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛‧唯的思想并末过时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.79,0:09:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙不需要武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.06,0:09:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它作为没被地球历史\N污染的空间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.80,0:09:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,曾经繁荣昌盛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.16,0:09:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为那是成为地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.56,0:09:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和平主义国家榜样的文化之源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.20,0:10:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成为榜样吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.54,0:10:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若宇宙的人再早一点\N听到你的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.64,0:10:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们或许会打消念头啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.14,0:10:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你告诉匹斯克拉福特先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.64,0:10:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星的人的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.45,0:10:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有我们为何一直在宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.28,0:10:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直在宇宙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.98,0:10:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对，联合被Oz推倒时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.19,0:10:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们曾经打算马上投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.82,0:10:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我们认为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.13,0:10:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那会对宇宙留下很大的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.90,0:10:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙卫星是靠精密计算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.50,0:10:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,造成的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.20,0:10:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个管理中心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.94,0:10:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必须维持着生活条件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.77,0:10:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,检查卫星的回转运动\N和大气状态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.41,0:10:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理天气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.25,0:10:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是以人手制造在地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.31,0:10:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常自然出现\N的现象的人工物体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.45,0:10:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这里环境生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.82,0:10:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,须要人类意识上的改革
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.79,0:11:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不安，对，如果不能忘记不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.00,0:11:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就不能在这里活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.57,0:11:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不安的人会拿起武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.30,0:11:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武器能消除不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.47,0:11:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去到哪个地步不安会被消除?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.04,0:11:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙进攻地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.34,0:11:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寻求稳定的大地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.45,0:11:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是Oz机动战士的运输艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.62,0:11:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们终于来攻击了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.46,0:11:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我一起迎击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.82,0:11:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.99,0:11:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球的亲善大使不可以战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.96,0:11:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会灵活运和两副面孔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.77,0:11:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在战斗中学会那种把戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.11,0:11:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.48,0:11:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.85,0:11:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.42,0:12:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是罗姆斐拉财团在宇宙制造的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.45,0:12:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD的地球降下计划图表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.82,0:12:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是一次解决\N地球纷争的作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.49,0:12:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有人都那样认为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.80,0:12:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没打算把MD派落地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.67,0:12:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若遵照罗姆斐拉的主义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.27,0:12:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球上只会流很多血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.08,0:12:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有力量的人统治地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.75,0:12:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们以为只是那样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.88,0:12:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球就会和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.92,0:12:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但大人否绝了统治地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.12,0:12:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯大人…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.79,0:12:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人一日不来宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.32,0:12:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世上就不会出现正确的秩序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.29,0:12:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的工作也完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.16,0:12:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.77,0:12:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校你还有身为Oz士兵的任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.94,0:12:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身为Oz士兵?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.81,0:12:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那结果会支持着大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.81,0:12:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,士兵对任务忠实就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.78,0:13:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校你已经成为\N超越士兵的领袖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.22,0:13:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，特校你优秀的才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.78,0:13:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要以士兵的身份被发挥出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.79,0:13:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并非作为引导大人的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.45,0:13:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是请你作为...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.79,0:13:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,支持大人的Oz士兵效力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.96,0:13:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作为支持特列斯大人的士兵?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.90,0:13:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人也应该希望那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.87,0:13:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯大人希望那样…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.68,0:13:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在联合军基地区
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.55,0:13:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD开始交战了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.62,0:13:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,600秒进入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.88,0:13:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴尔吉雷射炮有效范围
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.19,0:13:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷射炮能给予\N联合卫星多大损毁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.85,0:13:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若能破坏动力部份和管理设施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.12,0:13:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一炮就能停止它的机能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.96,0:13:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.06,0:13:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听闻那个卫星除了军人外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.23,0:13:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也有很多平民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.23,0:13:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是文职人员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.67,0:13:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们清楚知道据守要塞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.23,0:13:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就会成为攻击目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.60,0:13:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这件事蕾蒂‧安特校知道吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.41,0:13:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是迪尔麦优公爵的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.91,0:13:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把他们和背叛Oz的杰克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.48,0:13:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起消灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.98,0:14:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去准备麦丘留士和拜叶特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.61,0:14:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等!特洛瓦‧巴顿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.48,0:14:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我禁止你接近机动战士闸门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.98,0:14:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不论敌我，我不会相信叛徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.06,0:14:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安特校\N也不知道这件事吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.03,0:14:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校为了和联合战斗出击了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.23,0:14:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切交由我指挥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.26,0:14:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,押下这家伙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.40,0:14:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作为Oz的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.00,0:14:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会做出越权的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.51,0:14:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我对于特校的掩护部队里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.04,0:14:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不采用拜叶特\N和麦丘留士的战术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.88,0:14:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,存有少许疑问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.55,0:14:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,士兵不须要多加思考
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.85,0:14:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想和平的事给高层就够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.99,0:14:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们追求的只是胜利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.62,0:15:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靠近点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.85,0:15:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用近身战弥补反应速度的差距
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.46,0:15:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!打中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.06,0:15:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,里欧部队损失50%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.13,0:15:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人陶拉斯全是MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.70,0:15:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是终防线20%被毁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.01,0:15:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的平民避难完毕了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.91,0:15:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，已经用大型穿梭机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.01,0:15:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逃到安全空域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.95,0:15:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但区区MD不能攻陷这卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.68,0:15:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oz的巴尔吉会作出最后一击吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.12,0:15:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星要毁灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.76,0:15:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么意思?爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.16,0:15:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,建造卫星以来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.99,0:15:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在战争里被毁是第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.40,0:15:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那有多悲伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.40,0:16:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有人类有须要知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.70,0:16:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把军事力量带来宇宙的我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.54,0:16:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及想拥有军事力量的卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.24,0:16:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要在眼里烙下错误的烙印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.81,0:16:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然也补偿不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.55,0:16:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我们的血能有用就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.12,0:16:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把爷爷你卷入这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.42,0:16:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.79,0:16:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那应该由我来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.89,0:16:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，金达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.11,0:16:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴尔吉能源炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.55,0:16:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们真的想击毁卫星吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.39,0:17:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯大人希望战斗吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.39,0:17:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能创造\N特列斯大人的未来吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.50,0:17:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只剩下战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.67,0:17:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗是唯一的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.41,0:17:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不战斗就不能诞生任何东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.48,0:17:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.08,0:17:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.35,0:17:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯‧马吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.95,0:17:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，我永远的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.09,0:17:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米利亚尔特‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.36,0:17:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听闻你在宇宙出现，我好高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.23,0:17:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Oz正在改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.03,0:17:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的力量不足够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.37,0:17:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉…不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.67,0:17:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类要走的路太任性了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.00,0:17:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到扩张的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.61,0:17:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会把人类的心遗弃到这地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.48,0:17:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为Oz的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.65,0:17:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并非是进行战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.01,0:17:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是培养有战斗心的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.58,0:18:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但战斗已经连人类也不需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.82,0:18:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我作为一个士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.66,0:18:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凭自己的意志选择了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.56,0:18:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反抗那潮流的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.43,0:18:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米利亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.96,0:18:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在的我没有力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.40,0:18:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,改变罗姆斐拉选择了的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.77,0:18:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能向了解我的知心好友倾诉\N我觉得好幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.60,0:18:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米利亚，有另一个了解我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.94,0:18:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是关怀我\N拥有两颗心的女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.81,0:18:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.55,0:18:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近感到不安的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.55,0:18:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没资格谈论未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.82,0:18:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜扥你，米利亚，替我救她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.73,0:18:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要为了实现理想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.07,0:18:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了特列斯大人而战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.95,0:19:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,联合卫星进入射程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.82,0:19:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能源炮发射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.28,0:19:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是!蕾蒂‧安特校还在战场!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.99,0:19:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧!兵士只要服从命令就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.06,0:19:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校会明白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.83,0:19:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.57,0:19:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个蕾蒂‧安应该会阻止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.41,0:19:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对卫星的攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.48,0:19:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她正在学习卫星的脆弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.29,0:19:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没打中?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.79,0:19:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,避过了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.49,0:19:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,带我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.56,0:19:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,带我去巴尔吉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.91,0:20:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校!你没事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.44,0:20:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.31,0:20:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尼哥尔，我以士兵的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.28,0:20:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上了很好的一课
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.65,0:20:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是上课的结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.45,0:20:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我身为指挥官不可以放过你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.75,0:20:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校…!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.19,0:20:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的行动是对的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.13,0:20:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我这行动也是对的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.51,0:20:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯，我才没有力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.74,0:20:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为在这场混乱的战斗里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.98,0:20:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只能走士兵之路啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.18,0:20:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉财团决定在月面基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.52,0:20:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,建造MD的生产工场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.25,0:20:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在月球量产的MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.59,0:20:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是用来对付地球的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.96,0:20:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了马上解决\N地球上的许多纷争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.26,0:20:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们想出从宇宙直接降下部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.56,0:21:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把敌人歼灭的战略
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.70,0:21:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得到最强武器的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.17,0:21:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朝着不须要士兵\N力量的时代前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.64,0:21:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不明物体急速接近中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.44,0:21:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.98,0:21:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是钢弹，我们被钢弹发现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.78,0:21:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杀死MD的技师长吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.05,0:21:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对我来说是琐碎的目标啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.45,0:21:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月面基地捕捉钢弹的部队来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.69,0:21:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无子弹，无燃料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.23,0:21:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且没剩下正常的推进机能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.46,0:21:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,技师长\N我的性命就交由你保管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.01,0:21:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,急速掉头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.41,0:21:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.17,0:21:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.48,0:21:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那部钢弹没有反击的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.41,0:21:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我对那部机体有兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.98,0:21:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想尽可能在月面基地检查它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.89,0:21:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月面基地有联络来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.12,0:21:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停止攻击并捉住钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.42,0:21:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.49,0:22:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多谢你，仁慈的技师长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.87,0:22:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪吒，我们一定要强大起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.94,0:22:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像有个工场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.74,0:22:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能在那里帮我们增强吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.74,0:22:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.69,0:22:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心血来潮的找人出来\N只因为天气好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.69,0:22:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我一直等不到人\N你以为你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.69,0:22:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你是跑过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.69,0:22:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那也是应该的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.19,0:22:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love ! 那个惹人厌的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.69,0:23:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉弄人  是因为心理有爱意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.19,0:23:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love !  老是让人挂念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.69,0:23:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起\N我不该说出强人所难的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.69,0:23:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.51,0:23:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,次回预告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.49,0:23:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了保护卫星，宇宙拿起武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.86,0:23:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然这是害怕地球来袭才决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.52,0:23:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但Oz在背后暗中活动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.86,0:23:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了阻止量产机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.06,0:23:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪欧前去破坏月面基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.66,0:23:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在和卫星的志愿兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.17,0:23:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希尔德的战斗中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.83,0:23:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪欧看见迷途的卫星的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.41,0:23:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新机动战记-钢弹W，第二十三话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.64,0:23:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,变回死神的迪欧

